@Node Intro "Mayland / Introduction"
@SmartWrap


@{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}


@{b} · @{ub}@{LIndent 7}  @{" Disclaimer " Link Disclaim} What I cannot promise.
@{LIndent 0}



@{b}@{u}Mayland@{uu}@{ub} is a very useful @{b}Reminder program@{ub}, with features as follows:


@{b} · @{ub}@{LIndent 7}  @{" Execute " Link Action} a command and/or show a message! Not only at the exact
event time, but also some minutes/hours/days before and after.
@{LIndent 0}

@{b} · @{ub}@{LIndent 7}  @{" Come Again " Link MLD} feature of message requester.
@{LIndent 0}

@{b} · @{ub}@{LIndent 7}  @{" Drag'n'Drop " Link Drag'n'Drop} events to quickly reschedule.
@{LIndent 0}

@{b} · @{ub}@{LIndent 7}  @{" Year/Month/Day Calculations " Link Action} can be inserted in the message
text, e.g., "I'm %y-1976 years old!" will always show my correct age.
@{LIndent 0}



@{b}@{u}Mayland@{uu}@{ub} is also a very powerful @{b}Calendar program@{ub}, containing such features as:


@{b} · @{ub}@{LIndent 7}  @{" Overview " Link MainWin} containing link buttons to the previous and next
months.
@{LIndent 0}

@{b} · @{ub}@{LIndent 7}  @{" Holidays " Link Holidays} can be defined, and are uniquely displayed in the
overview.
@{LIndent 0}

@{b} · @{ub}@{LIndent 7}  @{" ARexx " Link ARexx} control.
@{LIndent 0}






		@{" ---> Install... " Link Install}

@EndNode

